				and quantitative finance. I actively develop my own trading strategies and help support my family's agricultural business fasui.it.
			</p>
			<p>
				From Latsch in South Tyrol, Italy, I bring a unique blend of technical expertise and hands-on business experience. 
				My multilingual background (German native, English C1, Italian B2) enhances my ability to work in diverse international environments.
			</p>
			<p>
