					<h3>Active Lifestyle</h3>
					<div class="activity-tags">
						<span class="activity-tag martial">ü•ã Karate</span>
						<span class="activity-tag martial">ü•ä Boxing</span>
						<span class="activity-tag endurance">üèÉ Marathons</span>
						<span class="activity-tag endurance">üö¥ Cycling</span>
						<span class="activity-tag fitness">üí™ Calisthenics</span>
						<span class="activity-tag music">ü•Å Drums</span>
					</div>
